Version requirements:

To run the program effectively the python interpreter needs to be version 3.9



For libraries that are needed they can be found below:

OS and Threading as the core libraries

Pandas and Numpy for data handling

Scikit-Learn for TFIDF vectoriser and normalise
Suprise for dataset, reader and SVD

Joblit to save and load the models

Tkinter for the Gui


Order of which the modules should be ran:

Filtering_Movie_Lens
Content_Based_recommender
Baseline_SVD
Recommendation_Engine
Hybrid_Recommender
Gui_app

after each of the modules have been run once they can be re-runed in any order